      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAGIC MIKEY (2) has been solid since winning three back, not handling the heavy deck two back before a solid performance on the dirt at Roebourne for the new stable last time out. Tsang's claim comes in handy and he should be prominent from the draw. Can get back to winning ways in the Cup. ANOTHER NEPHEW (4) has gone under narrowly his past couple, missing in a photo finish at Port Hedland last time out. Drawn awkwardly, but he's racing well without winning after jumping the equal favourite last time out. Can go one better. MYSTICAL MAN (7) jumped a $14 chance last start at Port Hedland and held off ANOTHER NEPHEW last start in a tight finish. Has to prove that wasn't a flash in the pan, though things look to set up similarly. Can get the job done. BEAUTIFUL BAROQUE (5) is third-up now and comes back in trip slightly. Drawn better now and can feature in the finish. REGINALD (1) was too good at Roebourne last start and can't be discounted.",
